release_note: Fixed a bug where the calendar didn t fit in certain countries. Fixed a bug where Traditional Chinese settings could not be set in certain regions. Other bug fixes and stabilization.
Fixed a bug where other diaries were displayed. Optimized file backup restore.
Chinese Traditional bug fixed. Other bug fixes.
Fixed bug related to sending mail. Changed some menu names. Other bug fixes.
Network optimization Stabilization and other bug fixes

Added dark mode function. Please use the Dark Mode button at the top of the More tab. Fixed a bug where the text color was only displayed in white in the timeline. Fixed a bug where the photo of the diary linked to D Day was displayed differently. Some UI layout changes.
Fixed a bug where the app did not run in some countries. Fixed a bug where the app would close when attaching a photo. Fixed a bug where photos were visible in the photo diary without photos.
Change the app name. Changed the way to change the app language. Added app introduction page. Behance Compatible with iPhone SE resolution. App stabilization and optimization.

Fixed a bug where the lock function sometimes did not work. Fixed a bug where edited photos are registered as originals. Fixed a bug that resprings when attaching a photo. Change the tab name. App stabilization and optimization.
Fixed a bug where iCloud photos could not be attached. Fixed Event date calculation bug. Other bug fixes and optimizations
